Shopgate,provides,mobile,shopping,solutions,for,commerce,providing,merchants,with,tools,to,create,mobile,shopping,websites,and,connecting,shoppers,to,thousands,of,shopping,apps,with,a,single,registration,The,Shopgate,Merchant,API,provides,a,developer,interface,enabling,orders,and,items,to,be,manage,automatically,Supported,functions,include,order,list,retrieval,with,filtering,order,details,retrieval,and,item,or,category,manipulation,The,API,accepts,HTTPS,POST,calls,and,returns,JSON,formatted,responses